race.description: Welcome To The Racing Season Maiden Hcp
race.comment: GANGGAJANG (4) makes her debut today as a 5YO, though her trials have been very strong at Belmont leading in. Clark has been on board all the way through and she remains in the saddle for her debut. Has options from the draw and she can make a winning start to her career. LACEY MARIE (6) resumes with a strong trial under her belt at Belmont recently. The form out of her most recent start was every strong where she wasn't disgraced at Northam when 30-1. Draws inside today and is not to be discounted. DASHING DIVA (10) has claims off a better run last start at Northam. POWER TO RULE (2) can improve coming back to an easier maiden today.
